descriptionHtml:
[center]This is the Preset for my Nord character Annara.
[b]
[/b][size=3][b]-About-[/b]
[/size]Annara is the preset of my old main character. I change her name because she originally had my own name.
Her face inproved over the year and this is the end result!

I have a version with blond hair and with brown hair.
The original had brown hair, but nords mostly have blond hair so that is why there is a blond version as well!

[img]https://s15.postimg.org/6szr8eh23/annara1.jpg[/img]

[b][size=3]- How to install -[/size][/b]
you first need to unzip it and than you need to go to your
Steamlibrary>Steamapps>Common>Skyrim>Data>SKSE>Plugins>Chargen>Presets
And all you need to do is drop the file there!


[b][size=3]- Trouble getting the face looking the same -[/size][/b]
There is a NIF file included, copie is and paste is in 
Steamlibrary>Steamapps>Common>Skyrim>Data>SKSE>Plugins>CharGen
Then when you're in game open the console and typ: showracemenu.
Now you're in the character creation all you need to do now is:
Go to sculpt and Import (Press F9) the optional file you just downloaded (the NIF file) and it should be fixed!

If you still have trouble let me know and I'll look into it!

[b][size=3]- Mods used and needed -[/size][/b]
